<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.3">
<l>umparumiv vēḻulaku mēḻkaṭalu mellā muṇṭapirā ṉaṇṭarkaḷmuṉ kaṇṭumakiḻ veyta</l>
<l>kumpamiku matayāṉai maruppocittuk kañcaṉ kuñcipiṭit taṭittapirāṉ kōyilmaruṅ keṅkum</l>
<l>paimpoṉoṭu veṇmuttam palapuṉṉai kāṭṭap palaṅkaṉikaḷ tēṉkāṭṭap paṭavaravē ralkul</l>
<l>ampaṉaiya kaṇmaṭavār makiḻveytu nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr where girls,</l>
<l rend="indent">with arrow-like eyes and Venus mounds like cobra hoods, attain joy,</l>
<l>Since on every side many laurel trees display [their] white pearls</l>
<l rend="indent">with fine gold, [and] since jackfruits display [their] nectar,</l>
<l>The temple of the lord who consumed all the heavens, these seven worlds,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the seven seas, the lord who, having broken the tusk of the elephant</l>
<l rend="indent">whose temples swelled [with] musth,</l>
<l>Grasping Kaṁsa’s hairknot, beat [him]</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the celestials seeing [him] before [them] attained joy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
